## Voxel Library

Library allows you to quickly import and export post types and all the different moving parts associated with a post type including:

- Post type configuration: Fields, filters etc.
- All templates associated with a post type: Single, archive, cards, submission etc.
- Taxonomies and their terms
- Product types
- Related post types

The library can be found in **WP admin Settings  Library**

Key features:

- Ability to export packages of post types, taxonomies, terms, product types and global colors
- Package importer with ability to pick and map only the data you need from a package
- Import preset packages featuring various post types from Voxel demos
